        [Zip Code City]
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        E-Mail: [Your E-Mail]<br />
        Phone: [Your Phone Number]
      </p>

      <h2>Responsible for content according to ยง 55 Abs. 2 RStV</h2>
      <p>
        [Name]<br />
        [Address]<br />
        [Zip Code City]
      </p>

      <h2>Disclaimer</h2>

